<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>上海市宝山区顾村实验学校</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201110/7b1ab7adc46b4b45bcfdc18c39b946ff.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
